<s> Unfortunately Word 97 treats this as an invalid character when reading HTML.  </s>
<s> I now found the place where the conversion from ' ' to '' should occur, and created a patch (which is attached to this mail).  </s>
<s> I didn't manage to compile Amaya on my Linux machine, so I cannot check if this fix is O.K., but it looks streight-forward.  </s>
